author: Hrishitaa Sharma
title: Alia Bhatt’s Bag Is Your Hump Day Treat
text:
‹ › 
We all know that Alia Bhatt is obsessed with cats. Apart from her zillion Instagrams featuring her two cats, even her closet is getting some cat love. Spotted at the airport, Badrinath Ki Dulhania starer carries an XL tote bag which has a cool kitty on it. Her airport style is definitely on point with a graphic tee-shirt tucked under her ripped denims. She causally throws on a denim bomber jacket and the bag, which complements her denim-on-denim look really well. 
All the cat lovers out there, don’t you think this bag is simply adorable? 1
